steps.html_instructions:
Turn left onto US-76 W/Elmwood Ave
Continue to follow US-76 W

Take exit 107A to merge onto I-20 W toward Augusta
Passing through Georgia
Entering Alabama
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-459 S/Montgomery/Tuscaloosa and merge onto I-459 S

Take the exit on the left onto I-20 W/I-59 S toward Tuscaloosa
Entering Mississippi
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-20 W, follow signs for Jackson
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-20 W

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-20 W, follow signs for Vicksburg
Passing through Louisiana
Entering Texas

Merge onto TX-31 W/TX-7 Loop W/Rte 19 N/State 19 N via the ramp to Corsicana
Continue to follow TX-7 Loop W
Slight right onto the ramp to TX-31 W/Rte 31 W/State 31 W/State Rte 31 W
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Corsicana/TX-31 W
Continue onto TX-31 W/Rte 31 W/State 31 W/State Rte 31 W
Take the ramp on the left onto I-35 S
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-35 S
Take exit 234B toward 8th - 3rd Sts/Huston - Tillotson University
